snippet.title: Speed Demons 2 - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Speed Demons 2 is an arcade highway-racing game coming to PC and consoles in 2025.  Wishlist it now on Steam:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2851640/Speed_Demons_2/

Speed Demons 2 features explosive action, breakneck speeds, and some very intense TRAFFIC. With a pulse-pounding soundtrack, unique side-scrolling perspectives, and TONS of varied modes, vehicles, and races, Speed Demons 2 is a thrilling blend of speed and chaos.
